@page "/"

<style>

    .f1-body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #121212;
        color: #fafafa;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
    }


    nav {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        background: rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.95);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border-bottom: 1px solid #2d2d2d;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        z-index: 1000;
    }

    .logo {
        position: absolute;
        left: 2rem;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #e10600;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 2rem;
        list-style: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

        .nav-links a {
            color: #999;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

            .nav-links a:hover {
                color: #e10600;
            }

    .login-btn {
        position: absolute;
        right: 2rem;
        background: #e10600;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    /* Hero Section */
    .hero {
        padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #121212 50%, #1a0a0a 100%);
        border-bottom: 1px solid #2d2d2d;
    }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fff, #e10600);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #999;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
        }

    .hero-btn {
        background: #e10600;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: all 0.3s;
    }

        .hero-btn:hover {
            background: #b80500;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }


    .tracks-section {
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

        .section-header h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

    .tracks-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .track-card {
        background: #1a1a1a;
        border: 1px solid #2d2d2d;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: all 0.3s;
    }

        .track-card:hover {
            border-color: #e10600;
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }

    .track-image img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 200px;
        object-fit: cover;
    }

    .track-content {
        padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .track-country {
        color: #e10600;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .track-name {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .track-stats {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        padding-top: 1rem;
        border-top: 1px solid #2d2d2d;
    }

    .stat-value {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #e10600;
    }

    .stat-label {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: #666;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    footer {
        background: #0a0a0a;
        border-top: 1px solid #2d2d2d;
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .footer-links {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

        .footer-links a {
            color: #999;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .nav-links {
            display: none;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
    }
</style>
<div class="f1-body">
    <nav>
        <a href="/f1" class="logo">F1 RACING HUB</a>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="/f1">Kezdőlap</a></li>
            <li><a href="/tracks">Pályák</a></li>
            <li><a href="/drivers">Versenyzők</a></li>
            <li><a href="/schedule">Versenynaptár</a></li>
            <li><a href="/news">Hírek</a></li>
            <li><a href="/regulation_changes">Szabályváltozások</a></li>
        </ul>
        <button class="login-btn">Bejelentkezés</button>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Éld át az F1 izgalmát</h1>
        <p>Fedezd fel a világ leglegendásabb versenypályáit, Monaco utcáitól a silverstone-i nagysebességű kanyarokig.</p>
        <button class="hero-btn">Pályák felfedezése</button>
    </section>

    <section class="tracks-section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Legendás versenypályák</h2>
            <p>Fedezd fel az ikonikus pályákat, amelyek meghatározzák a Forma-1-es versenyzést</p>
        </div>

        <div class="tracks-grid">
            <article class="track-card">
                <div class="track-image">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1568605117036-5fe5e7bab0b7?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Monaco">
                </div>
                <div class="track-content">
                    <div class="track-country">Monaco</div>
                    <h3 class="track-name">Circuit de Monaco</h3>
                    <p>Az F1 koronaékszere, Monaco szűk utcai pályája precizitást és bátorságot követel.</p>
                    <div class="track-stats">
                        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value">3.337 km</div><div class="stat-label">Hossz</div></div>
                        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value">78</div><div class="stat-label">Körök</div></div>
                        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value">19</div><div class="stat-label">Kanyarok</div></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="track-card">
                <div class="track-image">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Silverstone">
                </div>
                <div class="track-content">
                    <div class="track-country">Egyesült Királyság</div>
                    <h3 class="track-name">Silverstone Circuit</h3>
                    <p>A brit autósport otthona, olyan legendás kanyarokkal, mint a Maggots és a Becketts.</p>
                    <div class="track-stats">
                        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value">5.891 km</div><div class="stat-label">Hossz</div></div>
                        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value">52</div><div class="stat-label">Körök</div></div>
                        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value">18</div><div class="stat-label">Kanyarok</div></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="#">Rólunk</a>
            <a href="#">Kapcsolat</a>
            <a href="#">Adatvédelem</a>
        </div>
        <p class="footer-copyright">© 2026 F1 Racing Hub. Minden jog fenntartva.</p>
    </footer>
</div>

